esty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1729742124/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/vtdrningqycwveau4wlh.jpg","caption":"Bright, open living room with expansive views, perfect for relaxation and entertaining."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1729742144/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/p8lj88abpttqcs1eriwv.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1729742144/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/p8lj88abpttqcs1eriwv.jpg","caption":"Rich velvet seating and warm, textured fabrics against neutral tones - perfect for unwinding in style."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1729742145/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/srjcqo7liugynww7g7ud.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1729742145/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/srjcqo7liugynww7g7ud.jpg","caption":"Elegant staircase leading to the upper level, showcasing refined architectural details."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1729742144/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/g4a7lajkn4hnaesgmgqw.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1729742144/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/g4a7lajkn4hnaesgmgqw.jpg","caption":"Intimate nook with soft upholstery and natural stone flooring, perfect for quiet moments."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1729742124/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/rca12nhl0qgrajlnrx8q.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1729742124/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/rca12nhl0qgrajlnrx8q.jpg","caption":"Expansive living room with floor-to-ceiling views and seamless access to the outdoor oasis."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1729742124/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/zmmry9aw6xhtwhtgw9ak.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1729742124/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/zmmry9aw6xhtwhtgw9ak.jpg","caption":"Stone-lined fireplace anchors a mod