os was taken in the winter. "},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797011/vke2kliojk0duruhtgfr.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/vke2kliojk0duruhtgfr?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Just as good as beachfront"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797012/vd8qct2ghfjcdgidkuwd.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/vd8qct2ghfjcdgidkuwd?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Mountain views are just as special as ocean views"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797010/t8qeftlx7qgr1lkuvd24.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/t8qeftlx7qgr1lkuvd24?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Dreamy swing on a beautiful aged Oak tree. Doesn't get any better than the Malibu Beach House."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797011/fwi85bu0ewph8dbo6bjc.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/fwi85bu0ewph8dbo6bjc?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Outdoor dining "},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797011/yqpwa3vexq75w9pcieta.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/yqpwa3vexq75w9pcieta?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Neighborhood shots"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1740108553/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/dntpfjoukkva3kcoasiq.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/h_200,c_fit/v1740108553/production/5aff29ca5e0f84006a37cb5d/dntpfjoukkva3kcoasiq.jpg","caption":"Discover the thoughtfully designed layout, offering seamless flow and comfort in every corner."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797011/z234prrseq1edlpjuvjt.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/z234prrseq1edlpjuvjt?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Lechuza Beach Access"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713797010/xytwslnf2kspqqbwzrup.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/xyt