ion":"Relax in the sophisticated living space with high-end materials and designer furnishings."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/ejhri8pog1huv9epca7k.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/ejhri8pog1huv9epca7k?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"The open floor plan makes going from the dining room to the family room easy."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/rpklp9cmx1cviam26rv8.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/rpklp9cmx1cviam26rv8?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Dine inside or outside, always with a spectacular view and calm setting."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/gr3bv3r2cgldlfhatbnd.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/gr3bv3r2cgldlfhatbnd?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Gather in the open living space for quality time together next to the cosy fireplace."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/efitarmuyz07vyhyg6au.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/efitarmuyz07vyhyg6au?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Open the large glass doors and let the fresh ocean air flow inside."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/faorpuefjgunoq8ejk0t.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/faorpuefjgunoq8ejk0t?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Gorgeous kitchen space perfect for warm gatherings."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/xeymp3aernccizxncpj8.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/xeymp3aernccizxncpj8?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Step into the spacious kitchen, complete with state-of-the-art appliances and plenty of natural light."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/ujqfquewd1bddcboifaf.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/ujqfquewd1bddcboifaf?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"The kitchen is private yet open, with plenty of space to cook up a gourmet meal."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/pntk80ff6ncorv7gwfec.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/pntk80ff6ncorv7gwfec?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Designed with comfort, style and relaxation in mind."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/ejgobtjsyvkkeswnouab.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/ejgobtjsyvkkeswnouab?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"If the evening air becomes chilly, move inside to the expansive dining table next to the kitchen."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/mtq5g4pz4npyhifqkmmt.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/mtq5g4pz4npyhifqkmmt?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Cooking has never been this calming, surrounded by views of the Pacific Ocean as far as the eye can see!"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/nykmx4tuprfeoenn2krk.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/nykmx4tuprfeoenn2krk?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Dine al-fresco style at the 6-person outdoor dining table."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/yth27tja7c7hjtsjkyl6.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/yth27tja7c7hjtsjkyl6?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"The outdoor space is perfect for entertaining!"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/grslqeaetticwjkco8xy.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/grslqeaetticwjkco8xy?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Bird’s eye view of the deck covered by a glass roof."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/m8sutyjijuhm0a06blhf.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/m8sutyjijuhm0a06blhf?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Sip on your morning brew on the deck with sunlight, fresh air and shade."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/