tions and custom touches make you feel at home."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796920/c4e390qzfbriwdxqwnzt.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/c4e390qzfbriwdxqwnzt?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Sleep soundly and undisturbed with black-out curtains for your comfort."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/necd005d0zq6jtq8vhf0.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/necd005d0zq6jtq8vhf0?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Plenty of space to get ready for a big day (or night)."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/yjez7nu5kaupr7fs8wyb.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/yjez7nu5kaupr7fs8wyb?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Soak in the tub or relax in the steam shower. Your stress will melt away."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/ci72ykabua8f6j95catn.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/ci72ykabua8f6j95catn?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"The high ceilings are lined with beautiful white wooden panels."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/qyhsomnmx2s444kaxqn3.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/qyhsomnmx2s444kaxqn3?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Enjoy your favourite movie or TV show while snuggled into the comfy blankets."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/hrwuai39nati2eemoekz.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/hrwuai39nati2eemoekz?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Jump into a hot shower and dry off with fresh, clean towels."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/cif171qztrvpz03fzsuv.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/cif171qztrvpz03fzsuv?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Each bathroom comes sparkling clean and fully equipped with conditioner, shampoo, and toiletries."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty