ery corner."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/ilmrypb4wzxa3qwmsn0e.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/ilmrypb4wzxa3qwmsn0e?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Drive up to your private beach paradise."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796920/pfkxofxt3ytizrlcsnfs.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/pfkxofxt3ytizrlcsnfs?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Professionally and exclusively managed by Stay Awhile Villas, with concierge services for your convenience and enjoyment!"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/lafaqdurm8erab9xtry4.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/lafaqdurm8erab9xtry4?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Breathtaking beachfront vacation home with convenient beach access for your enjoyment."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/ffmeidfq37hwmp2vksjx.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/ffmeidfq37hwmp2vksjx?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Situated in a guard-gated and secure neighbourhood."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/aykauwyyyg8zcx2ctc2z.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/aykauwyyyg8zcx2ctc2z?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Smell the fresh sea air and gaze at the beautiful blue Pacific Ocean."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/msepycgdd5wsbi8tu96k.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/msepycgdd5wsbi8tu96k?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Paradise Cove is a speck of nostalgia on the otherwise glitzy and developed Malibu coast and beach district."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/txoyqwwvpypmeiw3c0c9.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/txoyqwwvpypmeiw3c0c9?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Paradise Cove Pier is a popular tourist attraction in Malibu"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/yxol4f8psfxlbnroowgc.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/yxol4f8psfxlbnroowgc?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"The Cove is best known as the setting for The Rockford Files (1974-1980), featuring James Garner."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/kkhggo3hduz5kzdapzky.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/kkhggo3hduz5kzdapzky?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"The beach at Paradise Cove provides a semi-private setting with less wind and distractions."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/gvugjvgwnnwrs7z9mg2j.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/gvugjvgwnnwrs7z9mg2j?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Paradise Cove Beach Café, just around the corner!"},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/prvwwxkdnvpxgtf8unra.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/prvwwxkdnvpxgtf8unra?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Paradise Cove has been the setting for hundreds of film and television productions across the decades."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/qr6vbjvkbfqsqirkz048.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/qr6vbjvkbfqsqirkz048?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Take a seat at Paradise Cove Beach Café for a refreshment and relaxation."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796919/dq8nxoyuakrcsudpc9ty.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/dq8nxoyuakrcsudpc9ty?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Surfside tropical drinks & American fare in an enclosed, airy cafe with some tables on the sand."},{"original":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/v1713796918/gmpuipimy4ivcqfgeesg.jpg","thumbnail":"https://assets.guesty.com/image/upload/c_fit,h_200/gmpuipimy4ivcqfgeesg?_a=BAMCcSGi0","caption":"Enjoy breathtaking views, incredible service, delicious food and a casual atmosphere."},{"original":"htt